    {
      "id": "smallBusiness",
      "type": "text-block",
      "fields": {
        "heading": "For Small Businesses",
        "body": "<div style=\"display: grid; gap: var(--space-2xl);\">\n    <!-- Step 1 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">1</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Create Your Account</h3>\n            <p class=\"mb-sm\">Register as a small business on CaltransBizConnect. You'll need basic business information including your business name, EIN, and contact details.</p>\n            <a href=\"register-small-business.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-small\">Create Account</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Step 2 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">2</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Complete Your Profile</h3>\n            <p class=\"mb-sm\">Add your business details, select your work categories and districts, and upload your capability statement (PDF, max 10MB).</p>\n            <p class=\"text-muted\">Tip: A complete profile increases your visibility to prime contractors.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Step 3 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">3</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Browse Opportunities</h3>\n            <p class=\"mb-sm\">Search and filter opportunities by district, category, and posting date. Each opportunity includes detailed project information, requirements, and contact details.</p>\n            <a href=\"opportunities.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-small\">View Opportunities</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Step 4 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">4</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Apply & Connect</h3>\n            <p>Contact the listed organization directly using the information provided in the opportunity listing. Follow their specific application process.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "primeContractor",
      "type": "text-block",
      "fields": {
        "heading": "For Prime Contractors",
        "body": "<div style=\"display: grid; gap: var(--space-2xl);\">\n    <!-- Step 1 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-secondary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">1</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Register Your Organization</h3>\n            <p class=\"mb-sm\">Create a prime contractor account with your organization details and authorized representative information.</p>\n            <a href=\"register-prime-contractor.html\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-small\">Create Account</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Step 2 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-secondary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">2</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Post an Opportunity</h3>\n            <p class=\"mb-sm\">Fill out the structured opportunity form with all required information including project description, timeline, budget range, and specific requirements.</p>\n            <div class=\"alert alert-info mt-md\">\n                <strong>Quality Standards:</strong> All postings must meet our quality requirements to ensure small businesses receive complete, accurate information.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Step 3 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-secondary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">3</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Search for Qualified Small Businesses</h3>\n            <p>Browse small business profiles, filter by category and district, and review capability statements to find qualified Small Businesses.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Step 4 -->\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: start;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 60px; height: 60px; background-color: var(--color-secondary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\">4</div>\n        <div>\n            <h3 class=\"mb-sm\">Manage Your Postings</h3>\n            <p>Track your active opportunities, update information as needed, and manage responses through your dashboard.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "help",
